{"tid":2030583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會 國安法 民意調查","createTime":"2020-05-22T23:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T06:32:42.000Z","uid":55597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2e38787cbbf8c3bbeb4a49d3023643ff33f0d99c","tid":2030583,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/98175365_269711067724961_6642923593422340096_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=8NoDVPTw33oAX-di3Mz&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=56cc7eb5c48ada22df6350131e8a0362&amp;oe=5EED4301\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F98175365_269711067724961_6642923593422340096_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D8NoDVPTw33oAX-di3Mz%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D56cc7eb5c48ada22df6350131e8a0362%26oe%3D5EED4301&h=c1ee8935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機會嚟喇飛雲！🔊🔊🔊🔊<br />\n（做完再share畀身邊朋友是美德吧）<br />\n<br />\n《国安法》講咗成日，我哋連PC都開埋，咁大家點睇？準備移民、練定紅歌、定係等国安嚟到我哋返屋企訓覺？ 😴<br />\n<br />\n民記研究團隊光速準備咗一個網上民意調查，希望收集大家嘅睇法，麻煩各位手足花少過10分鐘時間表達你嘅意見🙏🙏：<br />\n<br />\n👉 <a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=e034ec11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a> 👈<br />\n<br />\n國際社會需要聽到我哋嘅聲音，雪地跪求手足幫我哋推到個個都做！得72個鐘咋！！！🙏🙏🙏<br />\n<br />\n(救救admin, 填完下面留返個cm「done」🥺🥺🥺)<br />\n<br />\nsource : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkercpc/photos/a.107767670585969/269711064391628/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkercpc%2Fphotos%2Fa.107767670585969%2F269711064391628%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=9b627236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkercpc/photos/a.107767670585969/26